data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of West Palm Beach! This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom gem offers the perfect blend of comfort and location. Step outside to discover your very own paradise. The large lot offers plenty of space for outdoor activities. The highlight is the sparkling pool, where you can unwind on hot summer days or host poolside gatherings. Situated in a highly sought-after West Palm Beach neighborhood, this home provides the best of both worlds-tranquility and convenience. You're just a short drive from the pristine beaches and the vibrant downtown area, known for its dining, shopping, and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to own this West Palm Beach haven, where every day feels like a vacation. Schedule a viewing today and start living the Florida dream!
